Adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK, 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020
Irin wannan yanayin na yawan kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya ya tabbatar da cewa, duk da cewa matakai sun bambanta daga ƙasa zuwa ƙasa, yaduwar COVID-19 tana gudana cikin sauri a cikin dukkan ƙasashe.
Bisa ga kwarewar Italiya, ƙasashe, asibitoci da rukunin kulawar gaggawa na likita dole ne su ƙara kasancewa a shirye don magance ƙaruwar masu cutar COVID-19 waɗanda ke buƙatar kulawa ta likita da kulawa ta musamman.
A ranar 31 ga watan Disamba, 2019, an bayar da rahoton wasu cututtukan cutar ciwon daji da ba a san dalilin da ya sa ba a birnin Wuhan na lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
A ranar 9 ga watan Janairun 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cutar Sin ta bayyana dalilin cutar a matsayin sabon coronavirus wanda yanzu ake kira Coronavirus 2 na Ciwon Cutar Hanyoyin Numfashi 2-SARS-CoV.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar sankara ta 2-SARS-CoV an san ta da cutar coronavirus COVID-19.
Shaida ta nuna cewa kashi 80% na waɗanda ke da cutar COVID-19 suna da ƙananan cututtuka, wato cututtukan numfashi ba tare da kumburi ba ko kuma tare da kumburi, kuma yawancin suna warkewa.
Kashi 14% na waɗanda ke da cutar COVID-19 suna buƙatar asibiti kuma kashi 6% na sauran marasa lafiya suna buƙatar kulawa mai ƙarfi.
Yawan mutuwar waɗanda suka kamu da COVID-19 a cikin barci ya kai kusan 4%.
A cikin wannan binciken mun tantance kuma mun gwada yanayin kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU/EEA) da Burtaniya da lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a yanzu a cikin EU/EU Economic Area da kuma Birtaniya da kuma adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Al'amuran COVID-19 a ƙasashen EU/EEA da Birtaniya
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya kara fadada yanki kuma cutar ta Corona ta kara yaduwa a sauran kasashen duniya kamar yadda kasar Sin ta yi.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana annobar COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A ranar 5 ga Maris, a cewar Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri da abokan aikinsa sun ba da rahoton farkon tabbatar da cutar COVID-19 a Turai, kamar yadda WHO ta bayyana.
A cikin Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai, an fara samun sabbin mutane uku da suka kamu da cutar a ranar 24 ga watan Janairun 2020 a cikin mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an sami cutar COVID-19 a duk ƙasashe 30 na EU/EEA da Burtaniya, wanda ya haifar da rahoton kamuwa da cutar 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727 tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019, wanda ya haɗa da kamuwa da cutar 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 a Italiya kadai.
Samun adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 da kuma yawan masu kamuwa da cutar
A Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), ana samun adadin adadin mutanen da aka ba da rahoton COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a duniya ne kawai daga tushen hukuma kamar ma'aikatar kiwon lafiya ta ƙasashe, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na yanki da WHO kuma ana sabunta su kowace rana da karfe 8:00 na safe.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan ne don kimanta yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU da Burtaniya da kuma kwatanta su da Italiya.
A matsayin mai sauya yanayin ci gaban COVID-19, mun lissafa gajerun kwanaki 14 na COVID-19 kuma mun yi la'akari da yanayin COVID-19 a kowace EU da Burtaniya a tsakanin 1 ga Janairu-15 ga Maris 2020.
Mun kuma bayar da adadin adadin wadanda aka samu a kowace kasa a karfe 8:00 na safiyar ranar 15 ga watan Maris idan aka kwatanta da adadin da aka samu a Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga watan Janairu zuwa 15 ga watan Maris.
Yanayin COVID-19 a ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai da Burtaniya
Tsarin ƙididdigar ƙididdigar ƙididdigar kwanaki 14 na COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai da Burtaniya gabaɗaya ya bi tsarin lardin Hubei na China (Figure 1.
A cikin EU da Burtaniya gabaɗaya, adadin kamuwa da COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu, kuma ya sami ƙaruwa mai mahimmanci a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (Matsakaicin Nasara).
Wannan ya kasance saboda saurin karuwar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai da Burtaniya sun nuna irin wannan ƙaruwar a cikin adadin waɗanda suka kamu da COVID-19 a cikin su.
Shafi na 2 ya nuna adadin adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU da Burtaniya idan aka kwatanta da Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu-15 ga Maris, 2020.
Wannan ya nuna cewa a karfe 8:00 na safiyar ranar 15 ga watan Maris, adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar a wasu kasashe 15 na Tarayyar Turai da kuma Burtaniya sun yi daidai da adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar a Italiya a cikin makonni uku ko kasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin mutanen da aka ba da rahoton kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU da Burtaniya suna ƙaruwa cikin sauri.
Bayanan da aka samu na yawan kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 sun nuna cewa wannan kamuwa da cutar na ci gaba a cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Wannan duk da cewa kasashe suna cikin matakai daban-daban kuma ba koyaushe suke da daidaito ba dangane da amsawar lafiyar jama'a ta ƙasa, da kuma ma'anar yanayin da kuma hanyoyin da za a iya gano marasa lafiya don gwaji don tabbatar da cutar COVID-19.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitocin yankunan da ke fama da cutar a Italiya sun bayyana halin da ake ciki cewa kusan kashi 10% na masu fama da COVID-19 suna buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani, kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ba da rahoton cewa asibitoci da rukunin kulawa mai tsanani a waɗannan yankuna sun kai iyakar ƙarfin su.
Bayanai kan shigar da marasa lafiya da cutar COVID-19 a asibiti da kuma a cibiyar kulawa mai zurfi a ƙasashen EU/EEA yanzu sun kai kashi 6% da 1% na shari'o'in, bi da bi (ba a nuna bayanan ba).
Koyaya, dole ne a tattara wannan bayanan a cikin tsari mai kyau har sai bayanan kulawa na yanzu sun cika, wanda ke mai da hankali kan adadin lamuran da aka ruwaito da kuma adadin mutuwar.
Wani bincike da aka gudanar a watan Nuwamba na 2010 ya nuna bambancin da ke tsakanin adadin gadajen kulawa da kulawa a Turai, wanda ya kai 29.2 a Jamus da 4.2 a Portugal a kowace mutum 100,000.
Wannan yana nuna cewa ƙasashe na iya samun ƙasa da ƙasa ko fiye da na Italiya (12.5 gadajen kulawa na tsakiya da tsakiya ga mutane 100,000 a watan Nuwamba 2020).
Yanayin samfurin da aka danganta da wadatar kula da lafiya, tare da ƙimar kowace ƙasa ta EU da Burtaniya ta hanyar yaduwar COVID-19 da ke da alaƙa da haɗarin sama da kashi 90% na ƙimar ƙarfin ɗakunan kulawa na likita, an gabatar da su a cikin sabuntawa na shida na ECDC na COVID-19 na hanzari.
Saboda an tattara shari'o'in a cikin EU da UK, kuma asibitoci da cibiyoyin kula da lafiya na gaggawa suna kula da yawan jama'a a wani yanki, yana da kyau a sami bayanai game da shari'o'in da gadajen kulawa ta gaggawa daga ƙamus na rukunin yanki zuwa matakin 2 (2-NUTS).
Kwarewar Italiya da yanayin da ake ciki a yanzu a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa cutar COVID-19 tana yaduwa cikin sauri a cikin EU da Burtaniya.
Kasashe, asibitoci da cibiyoyin kula da gaggawa suna buƙatar shirya kansu don yanayin ci gaba da watsa kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 a cikin al'umma da kuma karuwar adadin masu cutar COVID-19 waɗanda ke buƙatar kulawa ta lafiya da kuma wasu daga cikinsu suna buƙatar kulawa ta gaggawa, kamar yadda ake faruwa a yanzu a yankunan da ke fama da cutar a Italiya.
An kuma bayyana a cikin sabon rahoton ECDC na gaggawa, cewa ana bukatar ingantacciyar hanyar magance cutar 2-SARS-COV, tare da sauya tsarin daga dakatar da shi zuwa rage shi, saboda yawan adadin da ake tsammani zai iya sa ba a sami isasshen lokaci ga masu yanke shawara da asibitoci don fahimta, yin shawarwari da daidaita martani idan ya cancanta ba a kan lokaci ba.
Binciken hadarin da aka yi a cikin gaggawa ya kuma tsara matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a don auna tasirin wannan annoba.
Yanzu akwai karamin taga na dama wanda kasashe zasu iya kara kokarin sarrafawa don dakile yaduwar cutar 2-SARS-CoV da rage matsin lamba akan bangaren kiwon lafiya.
Idan wannan ya gaza, tsarin kiwon lafiya na sauran kasashen Tarayyar Turai zai iya fuskantar matsalar rashin lafiyar da ke bukatar kulawa mai tsanani a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar cutar coronavirus ta 2019 ((19-COVID), wadda ta haifar da cutar coronavirus ta 2 (2-SARS-CoV) mai dauke da cutar sankarar numfashi (SARS) ta kashe mutane sama da 3,000 a China da sauran kasashen duniya, kuma ta cutar da mutane sama da 80,000, wanda hakan na iya zama bala'i ga bil'adama.
Kamar kwayar cutar SARS-CoV, wacce ta kamu da dubban mutane a 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya zama mai watsawa daga batsa kuma yana haifar da bayyanar cututtuka ta hanyar irin wannan tsari.
COVID-19 yana da ƙarancin ƙarfi da ƙarancin mutuwa fiye da SARS, amma yawan watsawa ya fi girma kuma yana shafar tsofaffi da maza fiye da matasa da mata.
Wannan labarin ya ba da cikakken bayani game da ci gaban bincike da sauri, a cikin martani ga karuwar adadin cututtukan da ke tattare da wannan sabon cutar.
Za mu tattauna muhimman fannoni na ilimin cututtuka, ilmin halitta, ilimin kwayar cuta, ganewar asali, magani, tsinkaya da kuma rigakafin cutar.
Duk da yake akwai tambayoyi da yawa da ke bukatar amsa, muna fatan wannan bita zai taimaka wajen fahimtar da kuma hana wannan cuta mai hatsari.
Bikin bazara na ranar 25 ga Janairu, 2020 ya zama abin tunawa ga mutanen China yayin da suka kasance a gida a duk lokacin hutun su na tsawon makonni da dama sakamakon barkewar sabuwar cutar.
Wannan kwayar cutar ta yi kama da kwayar cutar korona (CoV) da ta haifar da cutar sankarar numfashi (SARS) a 2003; saboda haka, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta sanya sunan SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, kuma ta sanya sunan cutar ta COVID-19.
Cutar ta samo asali ne daga birnin Wuhan na kasar Sin kuma ta yadu cikin sauri a duk fadin kasar da kuma kasashe kusan 50 a duniya.
A ranar 2 ga Maris, 2020, cutar ta sami 80,000 da aka tabbatar da cutar ta COVID-19, daga cikinsu 40,000 sun warke kuma sama da 3,000 sun mutu.
WHO ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 "magabcin jama'a na lamba 1" ne kuma ya fi ta'addanci ƙarfi.
A cewar PubMed(https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), a cikin ƙasa da watanni biyu, an buga sama da labarai 200 game da COVID-19 waɗanda suka haɗa da fannonin gano kwayar cuta, ilimin cuta, ilimin dalilai, ganowa da maganin cutar tun bayan an fara sanar da cutar a ranar 7 ga Janairu, 2020, kuma sun gano jerin kwayoyin cutar a cikin marasa lafiya daban-daban.
Wannan bita yana ƙoƙari ya nuna yanayin binciken a cikin sabon mujallar da ke saurin haɓaka.
A duk lokacin da ya fara, muna kokarin kwatanta COVID-19 da SARS da sauran cututtukan coronavirus da kuma cututtukan cututtukan numfashi na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS, 2012).
Za mu kuma tattauna abin da muka sani game da rigakafin cutar da kuma hasashen da ake yi, da kuma wasu tambayoyi masu gaggawa da ba a amsa ba.
Coronavirus an saba da shi azaman mai cutarwa ga mutane ba tare da haihuwa ba kuma yana haifar da kusan kashi 15% na kamuwa da cutar ta 4 na kowa.
Duk da haka, a wannan karni, mun fuskanci kwayar cutar coronavirus ta mutum sau biyu, SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, wanda ya haifar da barkewar cutar a China a 2003 da Saudiyya a 2012, kuma da sauri ya bazu a ƙasashe da yawa na duniya, tare da mummunan kamuwa da mutuwa.
Wannan ya sa COVID-19 ta zama ta uku a cikin tarihin ɗan adam.
An kuma nuna a hoto na 1.1, an fara sanar da cutar ta numfashi mai saurin kamuwa da cuta a Wuhan a ranar 31 ga watan Disamba, 2019 a hukumar lafiya ta kasar Sin.
Bayan mako guda, an fitar da jerin kwayoyin cutar coronavirus.
An samu mutuwar farko a birnin Wuhan a ranar 15 ga watan Janairun 2020.
A lokacin, cutar ta bazu cikin sauri zuwa garuruwa, larduna da ƙasashe masu kusa.
A ranar 20 ga watan Janairu, an samu rahoton kamuwa da cutar a tsakanin ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya, inda aka nuna cewa cutar tana iya yaduwa daga mutum zuwa mutum.
A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, an sanya birnin Wuhan a cikin keɓewa kuma an dakatar da dukkan hanyoyin sufuri na jama'a.
A ranar 24 ga watan Disamba, binciken farko na likita ya bayyana cewa daga cikin 41 da aka tabbatar da cutar, mutane 21 ne kawai suka sami hulɗa kai tsaye da kasuwar abincin teku, wanda ya zama farkon gano asalin cutar daga asalin dabba da ba a sani ba.
A ranar 30 ga watan Janairu, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ayyana barkewar cutar a matsayin gaggawa ta duniya.
A lokacin wannan rahoton, cutar ta bazu a duk ƙasar Sin da kusan ƙasashe 50 na duniya.
Saboda yanayin yana ci gaba da sauri, ƙarshen tsawon lokaci da kuma tsananin haɗin kai ya kasance a buɗe.
A ranar 11 ga watan Fabrairun 2020, an gudanar da bincike mai zurfi kan marasa lafiya 8,866 inda mutane 4,021 suka tabbatar da cewa suna da cutar COVID-19 wanda ya nuna sabon hoto na yaduwar cutar kamar haka (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/Ul-Bi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 ya kamu da mutane a kowane zamani, amma mafi yawansu suna tsakanin shekaru 30-65.
Kusan rabin (47.7%) na waɗanda suka kamu da cutar sun haura shekaru 50, kaɗan ne ke ƙasa da shekaru 20, kuma 14 ne kawai ke ƙasa da shekaru 10.
Yawan kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 ya fi na maza (0.31/100,000) fiye da na mata (0.27/100,000).
An samu barkewar cutar COVID-19 a cikin Hubei da kewayenta.
COVID-19 yana ɗaukar matsakaicin kwanaki 5 (9-2) kafin a gano mutum.
Matsakaicin lokaci tsakanin kamuwa da cutar zuwa bayyanar cutar shine kwanaki 4.8 (7.2-3.0).
A matsakaici, mutum yana mutuwa a cikin kwanaki 9.5 (13-4.8).
Matsakaicin R0 na cutar ya kasance 3.77 (95% CI:3.51-4.05), kuma daidaitaccen R0 ya kasance 4.82-2.32.
Adadin masu kamuwa da cutar ya karu sosai kafin 23 ga Disamba, wanda ya yi daidai da yawan zirga-zirgar mutane da kuma zirga-zirgar jama'a kafin bikin bazara na kasar Sin.
Yawan mutuwar da aka tabbatar da su ya kai 1.44% (95% CI:1.10-1.86%) da kuma yawan mutuwar da aka shirya a cikin dukkan masu kamuwa da cutar ya kai 3.06% (95% CI:2.02-4.59%).
Manyan dalilai uku na haɗarin COVID-19 sune jinsi (maza), shekaru (sama da 60), da kuma cututtukan numfashi.
Kwayar cutar korona ta kasance cikin babban kwayar cutar da ke dauke da RNA guda daya.
Ana iya rarraba kwayar cutar zuwa nau'i hudu, wato alpha, beta, gamma da delta. Wanda nau'i biyu na alpha da beta corona zasu iya cutar da mutane.
A cikin SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV coronaviruses, glycoprotein spike (S) yana da alaƙa da mai karɓar enzyme mai canza angiotensin 2 (ACE2) da kuma peptide peptide 4 (DPP4), wanda ke haifar da rikicewar membrane.
