Babban Daraktan Hukumar Kula da Lafiya ta Duniya Tedros Adhanom ya ce sanarwar gaggawa ta kiwon lafiya ta kasa ta samo asali ne daga "tsoron barkewar cutar a duniya, musamman a kasashe masu tasowa da matsakaitan cibiyoyin kiwon lafiya wadanda ba su da ingantacciyar tsarin kiwon lafiya".
