A halin yanzu, babu wata hujja da ke nuna cewa ana iya yin amfani da maganin rigakafi ko kuma magungunan kashe ƙwayoyin cuta don kare rigakafin kwayoyin cuta a cikin yanayi.
Koyaya, sabulun antibacterial sun haɗa da magungunan antibacterial na yau da kullun kamar su antibacterial, wanda ke da jerin nau'ikan rigakafin gabobin.
Saboda haka, ko da ba a ba da nau'ikan rigakafin antibacterial ga sabulun antibacterial ba, mai yiwuwa ba zai zama mai tasiri kamar yadda aka tallata ba.
Tare da sabulu da kayan aikin kare fata, kayan kwalliyar na iya haɗawa da acid (acetic acid, ascorbic acid, lactic acid) kamar pH regulator, benzoic acid mai aiki da kwayoyin cuta da masu taimakawa fata (alone vera, bitamin, mensoles, tsire-tsire na shuka). Wani bincike mai zurfi daga Jami'ar Oregon School of Public Health ya nuna cewa sabulu na yau da kullun kamar sabulu mai aiki da kwayoyin cuta yana da tasirin anti-microbial tare da hanawa da hana ƙwayoyin cuta a hannu.
