Ya sabawa ka'idar kasa duk da haka. Gwaje-gwajen kimiyya sun nuna cewa amfani da ruwan zafi ba shi da tasiri wajen kawar da kwayoyin cuta a hannu.
Ruwan wanke hannu ko kayan tsabtace hannu shine mai tsabtace hannu ba tare da amfani da ruwa ba.
A ƙarshen shekarun 1990 da farkon ƙarni na 21, maganin wanke hannu na giya ba tare da amfani da ruwa ba (wanda kuma aka sani da maganin wanke hannu na giya, mai tsabtace giya, mai tsabtace hannu) ya zama sananne ga jama'a.
Yawancin su suna dogara ne akan isopropyl ko ethanol da aka haɗa tare da kayan tsabtace microbial kamar carbomer (polymer na acrylic acid) don cakuda, ko kuma mai amfani kamar glycerin don ruwa, ko kuma mai sauƙin amfani da kumfa ko don rage tasirin busar da giya.
Ƙara oxygen zuwa ZOXID yana ƙara aikin antimicrobial. Tsabtace hannu yana ƙunshe da aƙalla kashi 60% zuwa 95% na barasa wanda ke kashe ƙwayoyin cuta masu aiki.
Maganin tsabtace giya yana kashe kwayoyin cuta, kwayoyin da ke da juriya ga yawancin kwayoyin cuta (MRSA da VRE), cututtukan tarin fuka, da wasu ƙwayoyin cuta (ciki har da HIV da cututtukan cututtukan mahaifa da RSV da cutar Reno, cutar sankara da mura da cutar hanta).
Maganin shan giya na kashi 70% na barasa, 99.97% (ragewar logarithm 3.5, daidai da rage 35 na murya) na kwayoyin cuta a hannu 30 seconds bayan aiwatarwa da 99.99% zuwa 99.999% (4-5 logarithm rage) na kwayoyin cuta a hannu minti daya bayan aiwatarwa, maginin hannu ya fi tasiri akan kwayoyin cuta kuma ya fi rashin cutarwa akan kwayar cuta.
Tsabtace hannu na giya ba shi da tasiri a kan ƙwayoyin cuta masu yaduwa (ko nau'in cutar Norocco), wanda ke haifar da cutar sankarar bargo, saboda haka dole ne a yi amfani da kayan tsabtace jiki ko kayan tsabtace hannu don wanke hannu ko rufe hannu.
