Ya kamata a wanke yatsunsu da kyau kuma a sanya su a cikin yatsun hannu. Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta ba da shawarar wanke hannu kafin wanke hannu da ruwa, musamman idan hannayen suna da ƙazanta.
