Babban haɗarin aiki a cikin ɗakunan gawawwaki shine ma'aikatan da ke shirya gawarwakin waɗanda ke da COVID-19 a lokacin mutuwarsu; waɗannan ma'aikatan suna da babban haɗari idan sun yi aiki, ƙarin kulawar injiniya ga waɗannan rukunin haɗarin shine sanya ɗakunan keɓewa ga marasa lafiya waɗanda ke da cutar ko ake zargi da COVID-19, lokacin da ake amfani da na'urar musayar numfashi.
Na'urar matsa lamba mara kyau don matsalar numfashi na iya zama mai dacewa a wasu tsarin kiwon lafiya da na mutuwa.
Dole ne a yi amfani da samfurori tare da na'urar gwaji na matakin 3.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta gargadi marasa lafiya da su nisanta kansu daga wuraren da ake jiran gwajin COVID-19 da ake zargi.
A Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, NIOSH ta tsara amfani da matattarar N95 mai inganci ko mafi kyau a cikin yankuna masu yawa, da kuma ingantaccen tsarin kariya na numfashi wanda ya hada da gwajin numfashi, horo da kuma gwaji.
Sauran na'urorin numfashi suna ba da ƙarin kariya da kwanciyar hankali ga ma'aikata. Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ba ta ba da shawarar sanya rigar rigakafi ba kamar yadda cutar numfashi ta COVID-19 take, amma ana watsa ta ta hanyar ruwa.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ba da shawarar sanya abin rufe fuska na tiyata kawai ga hukumar kula da marasa lafiya.
Ga waɗanda ke tattara alamun cututtukan numfashi a cikin kulawa da jigilar marasa lafiya na COVID-19 ba tare da na'urar musayar iska ba, WHO ta ba da shawarar sanya abin rufe fuska, tabarau, kariya ta fuska, rigar likita da safofin hannu.
Idan ana amfani da na'urar musayar numfashi, ana canza abin rufe fuska na tiyata zuwa N95 ko FFP2.
Ganin cewa an amince da taimakon PPE na duniya, WHO ta ba da shawarar rage bukatun PPE don isar da bayanai, shinge na likita kamar windows, ba da izinin shiga dakin marasa lafiya na COVID-19, kawai amfani da kayan aikin PPE na musamman, ci gaba da amfani da kayan aikin numfashi iri ɗaya ba tare da cirewa ba yayin lura da marasa lafiya ta hanyar gano cutar, saka idanu da daidaita jerin kayan aikin PPE, da kuma ba da shawarar yin amfani da abin rufe fuska ga mutanen da ba su da alamun cutar.
