Enzyme mai hana hawan jini 2 (ACE2) shine enzyme wanda ke rufe kwayar halitta a cikin huhu, jijiyoyi, zuciya, koda, da hanji.
ACE2 yana hana aikin enzyme mai suna angiotensin-containing (ACE) ta hanyar rage yawan kwayar cutar ta angiotensin da kuma kara yawan Ang (((1-7), wanda ake tsammanin zai iya zama magani mai kyau don magance cututtukan zuciya. ACE2 kuma yana da amfani a matsayin ƙofar shiga cikin ƙwayoyin cuta ga wasu coronaviruses.
Tsarin ɗan adam na enzyme yana bayyana mafi yawa azaman hACE2.
Zinc-binary angiotensin yana dauke da zinc-metal wanda yake bayyana a cikin ciki na ciki na tubes da sauran kwayoyin.
Kwayar ACE2 tana kunshe da mai ɗaukar N na yankin M2 peptide mai ɗaukar hoto da mai ɗaukar C wanda ke da alaƙa da amino acid mai ɗaukar nauyi.
ACE shine nau'in nau'in I-protein, tare da enzyme mai aiki akan ƙwayoyin mai karɓa a saman ƙwayoyin huhu da sauran ƙwayoyin cuta.
Kwayar halitta ta sha kashi na ACE2 wanda aka ware daga babban sinadarin P wanda ake kira shades, kuma ya zama mai karfafawa a cikin jini kuma ya rabu da shi sosai kuma ya fita daga cikin fitsari.
ACE2 yana cikin yawancin gabobin jiki: ACE2 yana cikin ƙwayoyin cuta na ƙwayoyin cuta, musamman ƙwayoyin cuta na C-type 2, ƙwayoyin cuta na ciki, ƙwayoyin cuta na ciki, ƙwayoyin cuta na jini da ƙwayoyin jini, da ƙwayoyin cuta na jijiyoyin jini a yawancin gabobin jiki.
Ana kuma samun ACE2 mRNA a gaban kwakwalwa, a tsakiyar kwakwalwa, a cikin kwakwalwa, da kuma a cikin kwakwalwar kwakwalwa.
Aikin farko na ACE2 shine daidaita daidaiton ACE.
ACE yana sanya hormone na angiotensin a cikin jini.
ACE2 yana aiki ne ta hanyar karboxyl-termial amino acid phenylalanine daga anigotensin II (Asp-Arg-Bal-Tyr-IIe-His-Pro-Phe) da kuma hydrolyses zuwa angiotensin (1 - 7, (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Lle-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 kuma na iya yin amfani da wasu nau'ikan peptide masu alaƙa kamar su - [des-Arg9] bradykinin, apelin neurotensin, dynorp hin A, ghrelin.
ACE2 kuma yana daidaita yawan amino acid mai ƙarfi na SLC6A19 kuma ana samun sa a cikin cutar Hartnap.
A matsayin furotin mai ɗaukar hoto, ACE2 yana aiki a matsayin babban hanyar shiga cikin ƙwayoyin cuta don wasu ƙwayoyin cuta na coronaviruses, kamar HcoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (wanda ke haifar da cutar SARS); da SARS-CoV-2 (wanda ke haifar da COVID-19).
A takaice dai, hada-hadar S1 na SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2 zuwa ACE2 na kwayar halitta a jikin kwayoyin, yana haifar da sauyawar kwayar cutar da kuma bin diddigin kwayar cutar da kuma kwayar halitta zuwa endosomes a cikin kwayar halitta.
Akwai tunanin cewa rage yawan ACE2 a cikin kwayoyin zai iya taimakawa wajen yaki da cutar.
Koyaya, wasu ƙungiyoyin ƙwararru da masu tsara jiki suna ba da shawarar daidaitaccen rage ACE da maganin ARB.
An gabatar da wani bincike mai zurfi da aka buga a ranar 11 ga watan Janairun, 2020 wanda ya gano cewa "An inganta amfani da ACE mai mahimmanci tare da mahimmancin rage haɗarin abubuwan da ke faruwa da kashi 34% idan aka kwatanta da sarrafawa".
Bugu da ƙari, "kasancewar haɗarin kamuwa da cutar huhu mai tsanani ya ragu a cikin marasa lafiya da aka kula da su da ACE inhibitors, ya haifar da haɗarin kamuwa da cutar huhu, musamman waɗanda suka kamu da bugun jini da kuma rashin ƙarfi na zuciya".
Amfani da masu hana ACE ya taimaka wajen magance cutar huhu mai nasaba da ruwa, kodayake sakamakon ya kasance mai rashin lafiya a cikin hadarin cutar huhu.
An gabatar da kwayar cutar mutum (rhACE2) a matsayin sabon magani don raunin huhu mai tsanani, kuma an gano cewa yana taimakawa wajen cutar hawan jini da rashin isashshen oxygen a cikin alade tare da lipoposaccharide - yana taimakawa wajen magance alamun rashin ƙarfi na numfashi.
